The paper focuses on Collaborative Filtering (CF) and its application in predicting user engagement on Twitter. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Social Computing (cs.SOC), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). However, given the emphasis on CF and ranking, cs.IR and cs.SI are the most likely categories, followed by cs.SOC, cs.CL, and cs.LG.
